        <p>Certified Translation is performed by a professional translation agency. The document carries the agency's letterhead, company stamp, and a translator's declaration confirming accuracy. It is accepted by private entities for internal and business purposes.</p>

        <h3><i class="fas fa-building"></i> When is Certified Translation Accepted?</h3>
        <ul>
