          <li><strong>Banks:</strong> Account opening, loan applications, proof of income</li>
          <li><strong>Private Companies:</strong> Employment contracts, vendor agreements, compliance files</li>
          <li><strong>Universities:</strong> Admission applications, <a href="/personal/academic/transcripts/">transcript evaluations</a></li>
